{"id":789547528,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"9 months, 4 weeks","timestamp":1662114161,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"12 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/789547528/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"45.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        if(s.length()==0){\n            return 0;\n        }\n        int max=0;\n        int start=0;\n        int end=0;\n        HashSet<Character> mp = new HashSet<>();\n        while(end<s.length()){\n            if(!mp.contains(s.charAt(end))){\n              \n                mp.add(s.charAt(end));\n                end++;\n            \n            }\n            else{\n                    max= Math.max(max,mp.size());\n                mp.remove(s.charAt(start));\n                start++;\n            }\n        \n            \n          \n            \n           \n            \n         \n            \n}\n       return Math.max(mp.size(),max);\n      \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false}
